# 0x15. C - File I/O
This directory contains functions on file input/output operations in C. The following fucntions do the following:
- [read_textfile](0-read_textfile.c) - reads a text file and prints it to the POSIX standard output
- [create_file](1-create_file.c) - creates a file
- [append_text_to_file](2-append_text_to_file.c) - appends text at the end of a file
- [cp](3-cp.c) - copies the content of a file to another file
